results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Pokemon Poke Ball
results.story: The Pokemon x Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Poke Ball’ celebrates 25 years of the iconic gaming franchise. An all-over Pokemon print is applied to the white canvas upper, lined in crimson textile and accented with a molded Poke Ball patch on the lateral ankle. Standard Chuck details remain intact, including a rubber toe cap, a circular All Star patch, and winged stitching atop the tongue. The high-top is mounted on a white rubber midsole with black pinstripe detailing and a custom Poke Ball license plate.

Louie Lopez Pro Mid 'Black White'
results.story: The Converse Louie Lopez Pro Mid ‘Black White’ delivers an essential colorway of the CONS team rider’s first signature shoe. The upper is constructed from black suede with butted seams and rubber backing for improved durability. Perforated leather is utilized on the mid-cut collar, while the insole features CX foam for lightweight cushioning and impact absorption. Branding elements include an embroidered Star Chevron logo and ‘L. Lopez’ stamped in gold foil lettering on the lateral side. Underfoot, the gum rubber outsole borrows the Chuck Taylor’s diamond traction pattern.

All Star BB Shift Low 'Black Neon Pink'
results.story: The Converse All Star BB Shift Low ‘Black Neon Pink’ showcases color-popped accents on a performance hoops shoe built with Nike cushioning. Vibrant streaks of color enliven the black Leno Weave upper, fortified with no-sew skins and accented with a pink Star Chevron logo on the lateral side. The low-top sits on a cushy foam midsole with a springy Zoom Turbo unit in the forefoot. A solid white rubber outsole features a multidirectional traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Crafted Canvas High 'Storm Wind'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Crafted Canvas High 'Storm Wind' updates the sneaker icon with an earth-friendly build. The upper is constructed from 50% recycled black canvas, along with 100% recycled polyester on the sneaker’s tonal overlays and contrasting off-white tongue. A screen-printed All Star patch on the medial ankle maintains the classic Chuck aesthetic. The high-top rides on a durable rubber midsole, composed of 12% rubber scraps for a uniquely speckled look.

results.name: Chuck 70 Crafted Canvas 'Natural'
results.story: The Converse Chuck 70 Crafted Canvas ‘Natural’ updates the foundational sneaker with a sustainable build. Constructed from 50% recycled canvas in a natural, undyed finish, the upper is reinforced with tonal overlays in 100% recycled polyester. Branding is limited to a One-Star logo on the heel tab and a circular canvas All-Star patch on the medial ankle. The high-top rests on an off-white rubber midsole, composed of 12% rubber scraps that result in a uniquely speckled look.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star Crafted Canvas 'Slate Sage'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Crafted Canvas ‘Slate Sage’ combines a neutral palette with a sustainable build. The low-top carries a grey canvas upper made with 50% recycled cotton, along with 100% recycled polyester on the eyestay, heel overlay, and tongue. Inside the shoe, an Ortholite sockliner composed of 75% recycled foam delivers lightweight cushioning with each step. The sneaker sits atop a speckled off-white rubber midsole made with 12% rubber scraps.

Chuck 70 Mule 'Egret'
Chuck 70 Mule 'Black'
results.story: The Converse Chuck 70 Mule ‘Black’ transforms the foundational sneaker into a convenient slip-on. Made with 100% recycled PET canvas in a solid black finish, the upper features closed forefoot seams to create a unique split-pattern design. Heritage details include winged tongue stitching, chrome eyelets, and a durable rubber toe cap. The low-top rests on an off-white rubber midsole, featuring contrasting black pinstripes and the Chuck 70’s signature glossy sidewalls.

results.name: Converse Run Star Motion Ombre Slate Sage Light Silver
results.story: The Converse Run Star Motion Platform Ombre ‘Slate Sage Light Silver’ makes over the iconic Chuck Taylor with exaggerated tooling for a fashion-forward look. Grey organic canvas is utilized on the upper, accented with a tonal rubber toe cap and a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle. The high-top is mounted on a platform CX foam midsole that pairs wavy lines with an ombre-inspired color treatment. A two-piece rubber outsole in grey and black features an aggressive sawtooth pattern that extends up the toe and heel.

results.name: Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star 70 Hi Come Tees Realms and Realities
results.story: Dropping as part of a capsule collection with the LA-based fashion label, the Come Tees x Converse Chuck 70 High ‘Realms and Realities’ features unique imagery intended to convey a stream-of-consciousness approach to design. A different digitally-printed graphic is applied to every panel of the 12oz canvas upper, including multicolor graffiti-like text and a black and orange tiger print. ‘Come Tees’ and ‘Realms and Realities’ are inscribed on the heel of the left and right shoe, respectively. Underfoot, the black and grey rubber outsole is updated with a unique ‘shatter’ graphic.

Krooked x Chuck Taylor All Star Pro High 'Triple Black'
results.story: The Krooked x Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Pro High ‘Triple Black’ delivers a skate-ready version of the heritage silhouette. A stealthy monochrome finish is executed on the sustainable rPET canvas upper, backed with rubber and featuring original artwork from Converse team rider Mike Anderson. Extra stitch lines wrap around the collar, showing where cuts should be administered for a custom height. Branding elements include a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle and a small Krooked tag affixed to the back collar.
